OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers vote to extend
OL,4,Cstrikes into September
OL,6,FBirmingham's bin strikes look set to
OL,7,Fstretch into the summer, after workers
OL,8,Fvoted to extend industrial action past
OL,9,Fthe local elections in May, and into
OL,10,FSeptember.
OL,12,FThe Unite Union says workers are
OL,13,Fstriking because: "Birmingham city
OL,14,Fcouncil has fired and rehired both
OL,15,Floaders (former WRCOs) and drivers
OL,16,Fonto contracts that reduce pay by up
OL,17,Fto #8,000."
