OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers vote to extend
OL,4,Cstrikes into September
OL,6,FThe union added: "Job & Talent agency
OL,7,Frefuse workers are striking over
OL,8,Fbullying, harassment and the threat of
OL,9,Fblacklisting at the council's refuse
OL,10,Fdepartment.
OL,12,F"Both sets of workers have voted to
OL,13,Fextend their industrial action
OL,14,Fmandate."
OL,16,FBin workers have been striking since
OL,17,FJanuary last year over a council plan
OL,18,Fto restructure the waste service,
OL,19,Fwhich they say would see some workers
OL,20,Ftaking a pay cut of thousands of
OL,21,Fpounds.
