OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers vote to extend
OL,4,Cstrikes into September
OL,6,FThis decision to extend strikes
OL,7,Ffurther would take the dispute into
OL,8,Fits 20th month.
OL,10,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,11,Fsaid: "Our members are more determined
OL,12,Fthan ever to achieve a fair
OL,13,Fsettlement, and they have Unite's
OL,14,Funwavering support. The council needs
OL,15,Fto get back around the table now
OL,16,Fbecause strikes will not end until we
OL,17,Fhave a fair deal for Birmingham's bin
OL,18,Fworkers."
